Now, there is one artist, in case you like artwork.

37:28.059 --> 37:29.381
I do, you don't know.

37:30.822 --> 37:31.983
There's one.

37:34.626 --> 37:38.550
Ah, silkscreen print by Colonel Rudolph Abel, A-B-E-L.

37:38.935 --> 37:41.438
Made while imprisoned at Atlanta Penitentiary.

37:44.561 --> 37:48.625
And this is an original painting by Dwight Eisenhower, Christmas 1960.

37:48.765 --> 37:53.110
It's extraordinary.

37:53.130 --> 37:57.955
Field of the Central Intelligence Agency.

37:57.995 --> 38:00.357
Remarkable.

38:00.397 --> 38:04.762
Washington Redskins.

38:04.782 --> 38:07.144
Okay.

38:07.164 --> 38:08.346
Colonel Abel.

38:08.446 --> 38:08.706
Colonel Abel.

