Yep.

39:33.781 --> 39:34.081
I know.

39:34.241 --> 39:34.802
Beautiful book.

39:36.065 --> 39:36.886
Jim's gone now.

39:37.147 --> 39:39.750
He's a lovely guy.

39:39.810 --> 39:41.293
Okay, I'm going to run along, sir.

